

Products - New Enterprise Stone & Lime Co., Inc.








































 











 










Products
From start to finish, we provide products for every stage of your project.












Aggregates
Our variety of aggregate sizes and properties are mined and produced throughout Pennsylvania and Western New York and used to provide safety, stability, and durability in road and building projects that improve our everyday lives.
Find aggregate products near you





Sand and Gravel
We produce manufactured sandstone and quartzite sands at several quarries throughout Pennsylvania and Western New York. In addition, natural sand and fine-sized limestone “sand” is available at select sites.
Find sand and gravel near you





Hot Mix Asphalt
Our state-certified plants and mix designs mean you get a consistent material you can depend on to meet your project specifications. The aggregates used in our mixes come from our own quarries so your quality assurance begins with the mining of the raw materials.
Find HMA near you





Ready-Mixed Concrete
We offer a wide variety of concrete mixes, products, and services to markets including heavy highway and bridge construction, manufacturing, commercial construction, residential construction, and small DIY homeowner projects.
Find ready-mixed concrete near you





Agricultural Lime
New Enterprise pulverized aglime is available in bulk or by the bag to meet the needs of farmers and commercial applicators as well as homeowners.  Using aglime is a key farming practice to ensure fertile soil, strong crop growth, and efficient, profitable farming.
Find aglime near you





Diamond-Tex®
Diamond-Tex®  is  a  Baseball and Softball Infield mix that has provided a safe and playable skinned infield surface for ball fields around the eastern USA. It requires less maintenance so you can focus on the game.
Find out more about Diamond-Tex





Industrial Minerals
Manufacturers in a wide range of industries use mineral fillers to enhance the quality and usefulness of products nearly everyone uses each day. Whatever the project, our mineral fillers can make a difference in your products.
Find industrial minerals near you





Soil and Turf Products
We are a leading supplier of compost, custom-blended soils, and topsoils. Each of the products is manufactured under strict guidelines to maintain consistent quality and to meet strict design specifications.
Find soil and turf products near you






