New Enterprise Stone & Lime Co., Inc. Reports Earnings Results for the Fiscal Year 2017; Provides Earnings Guidance for the Full Year 2018
Jun 1 17
New Enterprise Stone & Lime Co., Inc. reported earnings results for the fiscal year 2017. For the year, increase operating profit in fiscal 2017 by 15% compared to 2016. Operating income was actually up 24%, and the operating margin for the year expanded to 12.1% from 9.1%.

For the year 2018, company expects growing revenue and operating profit by mid-single digits in fiscal 2018 compared to fiscal 2017. Finally, company expects debt levels at the end of the year to be below those at the beginning of the year.


